postcontent:
The 4506 is the best pistol Smith & Wesson has ever made.  Never jams and is practically indestructible . . . more reliable than Glock.  Heavy stainless steel frame keeps recoil soft and permits use of +P ammunition.  5" barrel ensures outstanding accuracy.  8+1 capacity, fixed sights, no MIM parts, very low round count.

This pistol is in very nice shape.  A few minor handling marks and holster wear, but no scratches or dings. Sights were touched up with Hi-Viz paint, but that comes right off if you don't like it.  Does not have original box or papers, but comes with a gun case, an extra factory magazine, 50 rounds of Ranger T-series +P law enforcement ammo, 25 rounds of +P Golden Saber ammo.

Asking 500 cash for everything.  WILL NOT SHIP.  Might consider swapping for a P230, or trading towards a P220 or ambi 1911.  Great pistol that belonged to my Dad, but just a bit bigger and heavier than I'm comfortable with.  Was shooting very tight groups at the range last week.  This is a great 45 for recoil sensitive shooters, and fits smaller hands fairly well.  Rubber Hogue grips can be installed for greater comfort if desired, and factory mags are widely available for under 30 dollars each.  These pistols run perfectly and never break or jam. Stay safe
